---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import BgGrid from "@/components/assets/BgGrid.astro";

const seoProps = {
  title: "Terms and Conditions | Self Labs",
  description: "Read our terms and conditions for using Self Labs website design and development services. Understand your rights and responsibilities.",
  canonical: "/terms",
  ogType: "website"
};
---

<BaseLayout {...seoProps}>
  <section class="border-white/20 border-b">
    <div class="p-8 relative">
      <BgGrid />
      <h1 class="text-white font-black uppercase text-3xl lg:text-5xl mb-8">
        Terms & Conditions
      </h1>
      
      <div class="text-white space-y-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-orange">Effective Date:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}<br>
            <strong class="text-orange">Last Updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
          </p>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mt-3">
            These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern your use of Self Labs' website design and development services. 
            By engaging our services or using our website, you agree to be bound by these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-3">
            By accessing or using Self Labs services, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. 
            If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not access our services.
          </p>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            These Terms constitute a legally binding agreement between you ("Client," "you," or "your") and Self Labs 
            ("Company," "we," "us," or "our"). Your continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">2. Services</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Self Labs provides website design, development, and maintenance services. We offer both one-time 
            website builds ($300-$2,500+) and monthly maintenance retainer packages ($50-$200/month).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">3. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Payment is required according to the terms specified in your project agreement. For one-time builds, 
            a deposit may be required before work begins. Monthly retainer fees are billed at the beginning of 
            each month. All payments are non-refundable once work has commenced.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">4. Ownership & Code</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Upon full payment for one-time website builds, you own the code and all deliverables. Self Labs 
            retains the right to showcase the work in our portfolio unless otherwise agreed in writing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">5. Design Gallery Disclaimer</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            The design gallery displayed on our website is provided for inspiration purposes only. The images 
            showcased are examples of various design styles and approaches, and do not necessarily represent 
            work created by Self Labs. These designs are used solely to demonstrate different aesthetic 
            possibilities and to inspire potential clients. Self Labs does not claim ownership or authorship 
            of all designs displayed in the inspiration gallery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">6. Maintenance Services</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Monthly maintenance services are provided on a subscription basis and can be cancelled with 30 days 
            notice. Maintenance includes updates, backups, and minor content changes as specified in your plan.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">7. Client Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Clients are responsible for providing necessary content, feedback, and approvals in a timely manner. 
            Delays caused by client unavailability may result in extended project timelines.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Self Labs shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising 
            from the use of our services. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid for the specific service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">9. Refund & Satisfaction Guarantee</h2>
          
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-4">
            At Self Labs, we're committed to your complete satisfaction. We stand behind the quality of our work 
            and offer the following guarantee on all services:
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 mt-6">Our Quality Promise</h3>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We believe in doing the job right. Every project includes multiple revision rounds and client approval 
            at key milestones. We won't consider a project complete until you're happy with the result.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 mt-6">Refund Eligibility</h3>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Refunds are available under the following conditions:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-eagle space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Pre-Project Cancellation:</strong> 100% refund if you cancel before work begins (within 48 hours of payment)</li>
            <li><strong>Early-Stage Cancellation:</strong> 75% refund if you cancel within the first week and before initial design delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Mid-Project Cancellation:</strong> 50% refund if you cancel after initial design approval but before final delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Quality Issues:</strong> Full or partial refund if we fail to meet agreed-upon specifications after reasonable revision attempts</li>
            <li><strong>Monthly Services:</strong> Cancel anytime with 30-day notice; refund of unused portion on a pro-rata basis</li>
          </ul>

