          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Web technologies evolve rapidly. We cannot guarantee that websites will remain compatible with future 
            browser versions or technology changes. Ongoing maintenance may be required to maintain compatibility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">16. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-3">
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, SELF LABS SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-eagle space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4">
