            <li>Your violation of any third-party rights</li>
            <li>Content or materials you provide to us</li>
            <li>Your failure to comply with applicable laws or regulations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">18. Termination</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">18.1 Termination by Client</h3>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-4">
            You may terminate services with 30 days written notice. For one-time projects, termination may result 
            in charges for work completed to date. Monthly services may be cancelled with 30 days notice.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">18.2 Termination by Self Labs</h3>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We may terminate services immediately if you breach these Terms, fail to pay fees, or engage in 
            abusive or inappropriate behavior. We will provide reasonable notice when possible.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">18.3 Effect of Termination</h3>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed">
            Upon termination, you retain rights to completed work for which payment has been made. We will 
            provide project files and documentation as agreed. Confidentiality obligations continue after termination.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange mb-3">19. Dispute Resolution</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">19.1 Good Faith Resolution</h3>
          <p class="text-eagle leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We encourage resolving disputes through good faith communication. Contact us at 
            <a href="mailto:support@self-labs.io" class="text-orange underline">support@self-labs.io</a> 
            to discuss any concerns before pursuing formal resolution.
          </p>

